data.name: Emberborn Fiends
data.tooltip:
Summons <d ref="duckiesHeroHellborneSummon_CreateUnit.spawn_count" style="Bold"/> fiends to attack nearby enemies.

Fiends have <d ref="duckiesHeroHellborneSummon_Unit.vital_health.maximum"/> health and do <d ref="duckiesHeroHellborneSummon_UnitWpnDamage.amount" style="Bold"/> damage per hit, applying soulbrand on the enemies they damage.

Summoning new pack kills all old fiends.
